{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-143-investigating-the-torricelli-point-of-a-triangle","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 143: Analiza broja Torricellija za trougao","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Neka je ABC trougao čiji su svi unutrašnji uglovi manji od 120 stepeni. Neka je X bilo koja tačka unutar trougla, i neka su $XA = p$, $XC = q$, a $XB = r$.</p>\n<p>Fermat je postavio izazov Torricellija za pronalaženje položaja X, kako bi p + q + r bilo manje/smanjeno.</p>\n<p>Torričeli je dokazao da ako su jednakih trouglova AOB, BNC i AMC izgrađeni na svaku stranicu trokuta ABC, kružnici koji prolaze kroz AOB, BNC i AMC sastaju se u jednoj tački, T, unutar trokuta. Štaviše, dokazao je da T, poznata kao Torričelijeva/Fermatova tačka, minimalizuje $p + q + r$. Takođe se pokazuje da kada je zbir minimalan, $AN = BM = CO = p + q + r$ i da se AN, BM i CO takođe sastaju u T.</p>\n<img alt=\"Jednakostranični trouglovi AOB, BNC i AMC konstruisani su nad stranicama trougla ABC; opisane kružnice oko AOB, BNC i AMC seku se u jednoj tački T unutar trougla\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/investigating-the-torricelli-point-of-a-triangle.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Ako je zbir smanjen sa $a$, $b$, $c$, $p$, $q$ i $r$, gde su sve pozitivni ceo brojevi, nazivaćemo trougao ABC Torricellijevim trougolom. Za primer, $a = 399$, $b = 455$, $c = 511$ je primer Torricellijevog trougla, i $p + q + r = 784$. Pronađite zbir svih različitih vrednosti $p + q + r \\leq 120000$ za Torricellijeva trougla.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3fc1000cf542c50ff0e","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301772,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-143-investigating-the-torricelli-point-of-a-triangle"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function sumTorricelliTriangles() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nsumTorricelliTriangles();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>sumTorricelliTriangles()</code> should return <code>30758397</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sumTorricelliTriangles(), 30758397);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName":"problem-143-investigating-the-torricelli-point-of-a-triangle","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":true,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-144-investigating-multiple-reflections-of-a-laser-beam","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-142-perfect-square-collection","id":"5900f3fc1000cf542c50ff0e","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-143-investigating-the-torricelli-point-of-a-triangle"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}